<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Erreur serveur - Cris et Ronronnements">
    <title><%= title || '500 - Erreur serveur | Cris et Ronronnements' %></title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 via CDN -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" 
          integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" 
          crossorigin="anonymous">
    
    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" href="/assets/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Skip to main content -->
    <a href="#main-content" class="visually-hidden-focusable" style="position: absolute; left: -9999px; top: auto; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">
        Aller au contenu principal
    </a>
    
    <div class="container text-center my-5" role="main" aria-labelledby="error-title">
        <main id="main-content">
            <div class="error-container">
                <h1 class="display-1 fw-bold text-danger" id="error-title">500</h1>
                <h2 class="mb-4" id="error-subtitle">Erreur serveur</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-5" id="error-desc">
                    Désolé, une erreur interne est survenue. Notre équipe a été notifiée.
                </p>
                
                <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-block justify-content-md-center" role="navigation" aria-label="Navigation d'erreur">
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg me-md-3" aria-label="Retour à la page d'accueil">
                        Retour à l'accueil
                    </a>
                    <button onclick="location.reload()" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg" aria-label="Réessayer de charger la page">
                        Réessayer
                    </button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mt-5">
                    <div class="spinner-border text-danger" role="status" aria-hidden="true">
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Chargement...</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <style>
        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .display-1 {
            font-size: 8rem;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .visually-hidden-focusable:focus {
            position: static;
            width: auto;
            height: auto;
            overflow: visible;
            clip: auto;
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>
